adept.module

Interface IConversationProcessor


  • public interface IConversationProcessor
    The IConversationProcessor Interface defines the interfaces that will be implemented by ADEPT modules that process CUBISM Conversation objects..

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Document process(Document conversation)
      This definition of the process method takes a raw conversation as input and returns as output an annotated Conversation object which includes the results from processing.
      long processAsync(Document conversation)
      This is asynchronous definition of the Process method.
      Boolean tryGetResult(long requestId, Document conversation)
      This method is invoked multiple times as a polling mechanism to get the output from the asynchronous process method for the particular requestId.

      • tryGetResult

        Boolean tryGetResult(long requestId,
                   Document conversation)
                     throws AdeptModuleException
